DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey, Janet. How're you doing today?
Not bad, just getting started on a new project. How about you?
Pretty well. I think I'm getting adjusted all right.
Ok, I think... It's always weird coming into a new company, you know?
That's good to hear! Most of the people around here are great.
I understand. Most of the people around here are pretty easygoing though. I'm sure you'll fit right in!
Yeah! You said most though... is there anyone I should be watching out for?
Yeah, everyone seems really friendly so far. I really enjoyed my first day!
Oh, I didn't mean it like that. It's just an expression you know?
That's great to hear! I'm glad you're enjoying yourself so far.
Of course. Well, I'll leave you to your work. Good luck with the new project!
Thank you. Well, I'll leave you to your work. Good luck with the new project!
I sure hope so. It was good talking to you!
I hope so too. First week jitters is all I guess. I think it'll work out though.
I'm sure it will. Let me know if you have any problems. I'd better get back to work.
